PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbpres: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbpcat: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>
PREFIX purl: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>
select distinct ?p ?o ?l ?id where {
?s a ont:InformationAppliance .
?s rdfs:label ?l .
?s ont:wikiPageID ?id .
BIND (rdf:nil AS ?o).
BIND (rdfs:label AS ?p).
FILTER NOT EXISTS {?s a ont:operatingSystem .}
FILTER langMATCHES(lang(?l), "en")
}
ORDER BY ?o ?l
LIMIT 10000

PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
PREFIX ont: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/>
PREFIX dbpprop: <http://dbpedia.org/property/>
PREFIX dbpres: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/>
PREFIX dbpcat: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:>
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>
PREFIX purl: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/>
PREFIX yago: <http://dbpedia.org/class/yago/>
select distinct ?p ?o ?l ?id where {
{?s dcterms:subject category:Smartphones.}
UNION
{?s dcterms:subject category:Tablet_computers}.
?s rdfs:label ?l .
?s ont:wikiPageID ?id .
BIND (rdf:nil AS ?o).
BIND (rdfs:label AS ?p).
FILTER NOT EXISTS {?s ont:operatingSystem ?os .}
FILTER langMATCHES(lang(?l), "en")
}
ORDER BY ?o ?l
LIMIT 10000
